WEBVTT

1
00:00:09.129 --> 00:00:09.857
<i>C'mon!</i>

2
00:00:16.369 --> 00:00:18.929
<i>Running like a fugitive.</i>

3
00:00:20.073 --> 00:00:22.132
<i>Being chased by something</i>

4
00:00:23.810 --> 00:00:26.472
<i>Inside my heart is pounding</i>

5
00:00:27.814 --> 00:00:30.442
<i>My throat dry like it's withering</i>

6
00:00:32.085 --> 00:00:35.179
<i>For no single one.</i>

7
00:00:35.855 --> 00:00:38.915
<i>To none does belong.</i>

8
00:00:40.260 --> 00:00:44.526
<i>This time is ours. right now...</i>

9
00:00:47.300 --> 00:00:49.165
<i>Unraveling the pain.</i>

10
00:00:49.269 --> 00:00:50.998
<i>Unraveling our hearts.</i>

11
00:00:51.071 --> 00:00:53.403
<i>Unraveling shadows</i>

12
00:00:54.941 --> 00:00:56.704
<i>Stifling our breath.</i>

13
00:00:56.776 --> 00:00:58.676
<i>Reaching for beyond.</i>

14
00:00:58.745 --> 00:01:01.179
<i>Tearing through the dark</i>

15
00:01:03.083 --> 00:01:09.647
<i>In fighting and in love</i>

16
00:01:10.623 --> 00:01:13.251
<i>To the distant light above.</i>

17
00:01:13.927 --> 00:01:16.896
<i>Yes. we are on the way</i>

18
00:01:21.634 --> 00:01:22.931
<i>I wanna rock...</i>

19
00:01:25.505 --> 00:01:27.029
<i>Rockin' my heart</i>

20
00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:35.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

21
00:01:47.888 --> 00:01:50.379
This is quite some fog.
I can't see ahead.

22
00:02:02.870 --> 00:02:04.599
The bridge should be visible soon.

23
00:02:05.673 --> 00:02:08.437
When we reach the side of the bridge.
we'll be in the Land of the Waves.

24
00:02:30.331 --> 00:02:33.266
Wooow!
It's huge!

25
00:02:33.734 --> 00:02:35.929
H-Hey!
Please keep it down.

26
00:02:36.637 --> 00:02:38.605
I took this boat out under cover of fog.

27
00:02:39.406 --> 00:02:41.772
And I cut the engine
and am rowing by hand.

28
00:02:42.543 --> 00:02:45.137
If they find us.
we'll be in deep trouble.

29
00:02:51.085 --> 00:02:52.052
Mr. Tazuna.

30
00:02:55.522 --> 00:03:00.255
I want to ask you something
before we arrive at the pier.

31
00:03:04.398 --> 00:03:09.062
The identity of your assailants.
and the reason why they are after you.

32
00:03:09.436 --> 00:03:11.063
If you don't tell us...

33
00:03:11.138 --> 00:03:15.871
our mission may end
when you make landfall.

34
00:03:19.546 --> 00:03:25.451
<i>The Assassin of the Mist</i>

35
00:03:38.832 --> 00:03:41.130
It appears I have no choice
but to tell you.

36
00:03:41.702 --> 00:03:44.170
Frankly. I'd like you to listen.

37
00:03:45.239 --> 00:03:46.934
Just as you said.

38
00:03:47.007 --> 00:03:50.033
this may be beyond
the scope of your mission.

39
00:03:50.945 --> 00:03:55.939
Actually. I am being targeted
by a terrifying man.

40
00:03:56.984 --> 00:03:58.474
A terrifying man?

41
00:04:01.355 --> 00:04:01.980
Who?

42
00:04:04.458 --> 00:04:07.916
You guys have probably heard at
least his name before.

43
00:04:08.862 --> 00:04:13.856
A shipping magnate
by the name of Gato.

44
00:04:14.168 --> 00:04:18.070
What? Gato... of the Gato Company?

45
00:04:18.772 --> 00:04:21.400
One of the world's richest men?

46
00:04:21.642 --> 00:04:23.735
Who? What?

47
00:04:24.878 --> 00:04:25.469
Yes...

48
00:04:26.146 --> 00:04:30.378
On the surface. he's the chief executive
of a shipping company...

49
00:04:31.819 --> 00:04:33.650
But underneath.
he is into drug trafficking

50
00:04:33.721 --> 00:04:36.884
and deals in contraband
using gangs and Ninjas.

51
00:04:37.124 --> 00:04:39.388
Moreover. he runs a despicable business.

52
00:04:39.460 --> 00:04:43.123
ruthlessly taking over nations
and enterprises.

53
00:04:48.369 --> 00:04:49.836
It was about one year ago...

54
00:04:50.270 --> 00:04:53.535
when that man first set his eyes on
the Land of the Waves...

55
00:04:54.074 --> 00:04:57.566
He used his wealth and violence
to enter this country.

56
00:04:57.745 --> 00:04:59.269
and before anyone knew it.

57
00:04:59.346 --> 00:05:04.340
he had taken complete control of the island's
maritime transportation and shipping.

58
00:05:05.586 --> 00:05:10.080
Having a tight grip on the ocean. in an
island nation like the Land of the Waves.

59
00:05:10.157 --> 00:05:14.355
means having control of finance.
the government. the people... everything.

60
00:05:15.496 --> 00:05:18.727
The one thing Gato fears...

61
00:05:19.967 --> 00:05:22.197
is the completion of the bridge...

62
00:05:24.505 --> 00:05:26.700
that has been under construction
for some time now.

63
00:05:29.977 --> 00:05:30.807
I see.

64
00:05:30.878 --> 00:05:34.712
Since you're the one building the bridge.
you've become a hindrance.

65
00:05:35.716 --> 00:05:39.743
Then. those Ninjas from before
were Gato's men...?

66
00:05:43.323 --> 00:05:45.416
But I don't understand.

67
00:05:45.726 --> 00:05:48.559
Your opponent is a dangerous one.
who will even use Ninja.

68
00:05:48.896 --> 00:05:51.558
Why did you hide that fact from us
when you made your request?

69
00:05:52.533 --> 00:05:54.160
The Land of the Waves...

70
00:05:55.135 --> 00:06:00.471
is a very poor nation.
and even feudal lords have no money.

71
00:06:03.243 --> 00:06:05.905
Of course. we ordinary citizens
have no money either.

72
00:06:06.513 --> 00:06:10.677
We cannot afford to make requests of
Rank B or higher...

73
00:06:11.752 --> 00:06:16.348
Well. if you pull out
of the mission when I land ashore.

74
00:06:16.590 --> 00:06:19.320
I will. no doubt. be killed.

75
00:06:19.693 --> 00:06:22.423
Killed sometime before I make it home.

76
00:06:23.464 --> 00:06:25.898
But there's no need for concern!

77
00:06:26.633 --> 00:06:30.569
Should I die. my cute grandchild
who will turn eight...

78
00:06:30.704 --> 00:06:33.901
will only cry his heart out!

79
00:06:34.441 --> 00:06:35.430
Oh!

80
00:06:36.310 --> 00:06:39.973
And... my daughter will only blame
the Hidden Leaves Ninja

81
00:06:40.047 --> 00:06:44.484
for the rest of her life
and grieve in solitude!

82
00:06:47.921 --> 00:06:50.788
Oh. it's not your fault at all!

83
00:06:57.030 --> 00:06:57.655
Well...

84
00:06:57.731 --> 00:06:59.164
I guess we have no choice.

85
00:06:59.433 --> 00:07:00.991
Let's continue as his bodyguards.

86
00:07:01.368 --> 00:07:03.666
Oh! I am most grateful!

87
00:07:06.507 --> 00:07:07.405
<i>I won!</i>

88
00:07:11.311 --> 00:07:12.835
We'll be arriving soon.

89
00:07:19.186 --> 00:07:19.982
Tazuna.

90
00:07:20.053 --> 00:07:23.079
It appears we haven't been noticed
up until this point...

91
00:07:23.857 --> 00:07:24.881
Thanks.

92
00:08:05.499 --> 00:08:06.761
This is as far as I go.

93
00:08:07.267 --> 00:08:08.097
See you around.

94
00:08:08.468 --> 00:08:10.959
Yeah. You've been a big help.

95
00:08:12.039 --> 00:08:12.835
Be careful.

96
00:08:25.352 --> 00:08:26.114
Okay!

97
00:08:26.186 --> 00:08:29.553
Get me home safely.

98
00:08:29.790 --> 00:08:31.018
Right.

99
00:08:31.892 --> 00:08:37.091
<i>When they next attack.</i>
<i>it won't be Chunin. but elite level Jonin.</i>

100
00:08:37.864 --> 00:08:39.297
<i>Cripes!</i>

101
00:08:51.411 --> 00:08:54.278
<i>I won't let this guy do</i>
<i>all the fun stuff anymore!</i>

102
00:09:00.554 --> 00:09:01.179
There!

103
00:09:14.101 --> 00:09:16.433
Heh... Just a mouse.

104
00:09:16.503 --> 00:09:18.767
Quit trying to show off!

105
00:09:18.839 --> 00:09:21.137
There was nothing there
in the first place!

106
00:09:21.408 --> 00:09:22.705
Please. Naruto.

107
00:09:22.776 --> 00:09:24.539
Don't use Kunai Knives recklessly.

108
00:09:24.611 --> 00:09:25.805
They're really dangerous.

109
00:09:26.980 --> 00:09:29.744
Hey brat!
Don't be doing anything confusing!

110
00:09:30.083 --> 00:09:32.176
Huh? I sense a presence there!

111
00:09:32.319 --> 00:09:34.014
No. over here?!

112
00:09:37.324 --> 00:09:37.915
There!

113
00:09:40.027 --> 00:09:41.619
Stop it. already!

114
00:09:44.331 --> 00:09:48.995
S-Someone's really been targeting us
the whole time!

115
00:09:49.069 --> 00:09:50.331
Yeah right!

116
00:09:50.404 --> 00:09:52.804
Knock it off. you!

117
00:09:58.078 --> 00:10:00.171
Naruto!
What have you done?!

118
00:10:00.247 --> 00:10:01.475
It's a bunny!

119
00:10:04.017 --> 00:10:05.075
I'm sorry.

120
00:10:05.152 --> 00:10:08.246
I didn't mean to...
I'm sorry. bunny.

121
00:10:08.322 --> 00:10:09.812
It's just a rabbit. eh.

122
00:10:11.958 --> 00:10:13.357
<i>That's a snow rabbit.</i>

123
00:10:14.161 --> 00:10:16.686
<i>But that doesn't explain</i>
<i>its fur color...</i>

124
00:10:17.864 --> 00:10:21.823
<i>The coat turns white only during winter</i>
<i>when there is little sunlight.</i>

125
00:10:32.479 --> 00:10:34.003
<i>Which means...</i>

126
00:10:34.081 --> 00:10:39.144
<i>that snow rabbit was raised indoors</i>
<i>without sunlight to be used as a substitution.</i>

127
00:10:48.562 --> 00:10:50.223
<i>Guess they're already here...</i>

128
00:10:50.430 --> 00:10:51.954
I'm sorry...

129
00:10:52.599 --> 00:10:58.060
<i>I see... The Demon Brothers wouldn't</i>
<i>be enough to take on these guys.</i>

130
00:10:59.106 --> 00:11:01.370
<i>The Copy Ninja from the</i>
<i>Village of the Hidden Leaves.</i>

131
00:11:02.142 --> 00:11:05.168
<i>"Sharingan" Kakashi is with them...</i>

132
00:11:10.117 --> 00:11:10.947
Everyone. get down!

133
00:11:30.871 --> 00:11:32.361
<i>If I'm not mistaken. he's...</i>

134
00:11:38.378 --> 00:11:39.470
<i>Here we go!</i>

135
00:11:39.546 --> 00:11:41.343
<i>Here we go. here we go.</i>
<i>here we go!</i>

136
00:11:41.815 --> 00:11:44.181
<i>I'm going to do it this time.</i>

137
00:11:44.251 --> 00:11:46.219
<i>I won't lose to Sasuke!</i>

138
00:11:47.287 --> 00:11:48.948
Well. well.

139
00:11:49.022 --> 00:11:52.924
If it isn't the Rogue Ninja
of the Hidden Mist. Zabuza Momochi!

140
00:11:53.693 --> 00:11:57.288
<i>Rogue Ninja? Whatever.</i>
<i>What's important now is...</i>

141
00:11:57.731 --> 00:11:59.028
<i>Ready...</i>

142
00:11:59.099 --> 00:11:59.622
<i>Go!</i>

143
00:12:02.602 --> 00:12:03.193
You're in the way.

144
00:12:04.304 --> 00:12:05.396
Get back. you guys.

145
00:12:05.572 --> 00:12:06.539
Why?!

146
00:12:06.940 --> 00:12:10.068
He's on a totally different level from
the guys from the other day.

147
00:12:12.746 --> 00:12:14.475
<i>His being our opponent means...</i>

148
00:12:15.982 --> 00:12:16.744
Huh?

149
00:12:17.017 --> 00:12:17.745
Oh.

150
00:12:19.186 --> 00:12:21.586
<i>That things might be tricky</i>
<i>as I am now.</i>

151
00:12:22.656 --> 00:12:25.352
I assume you are Kakashi.
the Sharingan user...

152
00:12:30.864 --> 00:12:32.388
Sorry. but...

153
00:12:32.799 --> 00:12:35.233
I'll have you hand over the old man.

154
00:12:49.917 --> 00:12:53.353
<i>Huh? Huh? Sharingan?</i>
<i>What's that?</i>

155
00:12:53.821 --> 00:12:56.289
<i>What? What is he talking about?</i>

156
00:12:56.891 --> 00:12:58.256
<i>Is this guy strong?</i>

157
00:12:58.559 --> 00:12:59.617
<i>Sharingan...</i>

158
00:13:00.127 --> 00:13:02.960
Get in Manji battle formation. you guys.

159
00:13:03.064 --> 00:13:04.429
Protect Tazuna...

160
00:13:05.933 --> 00:13:07.924
Don't involve yourselves in the fight.

161
00:13:08.169 --> 00:13:08.635
Huh?

162
00:13:09.537 --> 00:13:11.664
That's the teamwork
in this situation.

163
00:13:15.943 --> 00:13:16.807
Huh?!

164
00:13:21.382 --> 00:13:22.679
Fight me.

165
00:13:24.785 --> 00:13:27.015
<i>W-What's this eye...?</i>

166
00:13:27.922 --> 00:13:29.014
Well now...

167
00:13:29.090 --> 00:13:32.685
I never expected to see
the rumored Sharingan this soon...

168
00:13:32.760 --> 00:13:34.022
This is an honor.

169
00:13:34.528 --> 00:13:36.894
Everyone's been saying Sharingan...

170
00:13:36.964 --> 00:13:38.022
What is it?!

171
00:13:39.233 --> 00:13:40.222
...Sharingan.

172
00:13:41.001 --> 00:13:44.027
Power that the light of the eye generates.
and the pupil emanates.

173
00:13:46.440 --> 00:13:48.203
The user of
the so-called Visual Jutsu (Art)

174
00:13:48.275 --> 00:13:51.005
Is said to possess the vision to see through
all Genjutsu (Illusionary Art).

175
00:13:51.078 --> 00:13:53.342
Taijutsu (Physical Art).
and Ninjutsu (Ninja Art).

176
00:13:53.414 --> 00:13:55.348
and is able to deflect them.

177
00:13:58.152 --> 00:14:01.553
The Sharingan is a type of eye
that is unique

178
00:14:01.622 --> 00:14:03.522
to the user of the Visual Art.

179
00:14:04.959 --> 00:14:08.793
However. that is not the only power of
the Sharingan.

180
00:14:13.300 --> 00:14:14.858
Well said.

181
00:14:15.136 --> 00:14:17.036
That is not all.

182
00:14:17.438 --> 00:14:20.635
What's more frightening is that
such an eye

183
00:14:20.708 --> 00:14:24.405
can assess an opponent's techniques
and copy them.

184
00:14:31.919 --> 00:14:34.888
When I was in the Anbu Black Ops
of the Hidden Mist.

185
00:14:34.955 --> 00:14:37.321
search information
about you was in the Bingo Book

186
00:14:37.391 --> 00:14:39.951
I would carry around with me.

187
00:14:41.328 --> 00:14:43.523
There was also something
else in the book...

188
00:14:44.198 --> 00:14:47.395
About the man who has copied
over one thousand skills...

189
00:14:47.468 --> 00:14:49.368
Kakashi the Copy Ninja.

190
00:14:54.975 --> 00:14:58.968
<i>What? Kakashi Sensei</i>
<i>is that incredible a Ninja?</i>

191
00:14:59.814 --> 00:15:01.543
W-Wow!

192
00:15:04.819 --> 00:15:06.116
<i>What does this mean?</i>

193
00:15:06.587 --> 00:15:09.249
<i>The Sharingan...is a special trait</i>

194
00:15:09.323 --> 00:15:12.258
<i>that appears in only a select few</i>
<i>even among the Uchiha clan.</i>

195
00:15:13.761 --> 00:15:15.353
<i>Could it be. that this guy...</i>

196
00:15:18.799 --> 00:15:21.131
Let's end the talking here.

197
00:15:22.002 --> 00:15:24.971
I must kill that old man immediately.

198
00:15:36.283 --> 00:15:40.947
But. Kakashi. it seems
I have to defeat you first.

199
00:15:49.730 --> 00:15:50.594
Over there!

200
00:15:50.664 --> 00:15:51.722
And he's even on the water?

201
00:16:01.675 --> 00:16:03.666
<i>He's building up quite a bit of Chakra!</i>

202
00:16:11.952 --> 00:16:14.819
Ninja Art. Hidden Mist Jutsu.

203
00:16:24.999 --> 00:16:25.761
He's vanished?!

204
00:16:28.402 --> 00:16:29.061
Sensei!

205
00:16:29.536 --> 00:16:32.130
He'll probably come to erase me first...

206
00:16:32.806 --> 00:16:34.296
What is he?

207
00:16:34.909 --> 00:16:36.137
Zabuza Momochi.

208
00:16:36.777 --> 00:16:38.870
He's a Anbu Black Ops member
in the Hidden Mist and

209
00:16:38.946 --> 00:16:41.744
is known as "the silent killing"
technique expert.

210
00:16:41.949 --> 00:16:42.938
S-Silent?

211
00:16:43.450 --> 00:16:44.883
As the name suggests...

212
00:16:45.419 --> 00:16:49.947
it's a killing skill that's implemented
in an instant in silence.

213
00:16:57.932 --> 00:16:58.899
By the time you realize it.

214
00:16:58.966 --> 00:17:01.127
it's possible you may find yourself
in the afterlife.

215
00:17:01.969 --> 00:17:05.166
I haven't totally mastered
the use of my Sharingan.

216
00:17:05.739 --> 00:17:07.468
So don't lower your guard. you guys.

217
00:17:13.247 --> 00:17:15.545
Well. if we fail. we'll only die.

218
00:17:15.916 --> 00:17:17.406
How can you be so carefree?!

219
00:17:23.924 --> 00:17:26.256
The mist is steadily getting thicker!

220
00:17:26.560 --> 00:17:29.051
The Land of the Waves
is surrounded by ocean.

221
00:17:29.530 --> 00:17:31.589
So mist rises very easily.

222
00:17:34.969 --> 00:17:35.594
Sensei!

223
00:17:46.313 --> 00:17:47.371
Eight spots.

224
00:17:47.681 --> 00:17:49.239
Huh? What?

225
00:17:50.384 --> 00:17:53.353
The larynx. the spine.
the lungs. the liver...

226
00:17:54.021 --> 00:17:56.546
The jugular and the subclavian veins.

227
00:17:56.890 --> 00:17:59.256
The kidneys. the heart.

228
00:18:00.561 --> 00:18:03.359
Now then. which vulnerable spot
would be good?

229
00:18:31.025 --> 00:18:32.686
<i>What an intense thirst for blood!</i>

230
00:18:33.961 --> 00:18:36.862
<i>If I take even one breath.</i>
<i>or move my eyes.</i>

231
00:18:36.930 --> 00:18:40.593
<i>I will be marked and killed</i>
<i>that's what I'm feeling.</i>

232
00:18:41.735 --> 00:18:45.569
<i>If I'm stuck like this for an hour.</i>
<i>I'll go mad!</i>

233
00:18:47.374 --> 00:18:49.365
<i>Facing a Jonin's intent to kill...</i>

234
00:18:50.344 --> 00:18:53.404
<i>This sensation is like having</i>
<i>my life being held in limbo...</i>

235
00:18:55.849 --> 00:18:59.876
<i>No way! I'd rather die</i>
<i>to escape this feeling!</i>

236
00:19:01.955 --> 00:19:02.785
Sasuke.

237
00:19:03.624 --> 00:19:07.287
Don't worry.
I'll protect you with my life.

238
00:19:10.064 --> 00:19:14.091
I will <i>not</i> allow
my comrades to get killed.

239
00:19:19.406 --> 00:19:22.000
I wonder about that...

240
00:19:28.549 --> 00:19:29.516
It's over.

241
00:20:00.447 --> 00:20:01.675
Sensei!
Behind you!

242
00:20:06.854 --> 00:20:08.185
Die!

243
00:20:19.733 --> 00:20:21.166
<i>The Water Clone Jutsu?</i>

244
00:20:22.870 --> 00:20:23.768
<i>It can't be!</i>

245
00:20:38.051 --> 00:20:39.643
<i>In this mist...</i>

246
00:20:45.459 --> 00:20:47.620
<i>did he actually copy me?</i>

247
00:20:51.899 --> 00:20:52.593
Don't move.

248
00:21:07.648 --> 00:21:08.546
It's over.

249
00:22:52.388 --> 00:22:53.650
O-Oh no!

250
00:22:53.722 --> 00:22:56.418
Even Kakashi Sensei fell under
Zabuza's Jutsu.

251
00:22:56.892 --> 00:22:57.586
I've got to escape.

252
00:22:57.660 --> 00:22:59.958
I'll get killed. for real.

253
00:23:01.263 --> 00:23:02.230
This pain.

254
00:23:03.065 --> 00:23:05.431
What am I doing?!

255
00:23:05.901 --> 00:23:09.701
I'd decided. hadn't I?
Not to run away no matter what happens.

256
00:23:10.773 --> 00:23:13.207
Next episode:
"The Oath of Pain!"

257
00:23:13.542 --> 00:23:16.443
I'm going to kick butt once again!

